{
  "stem": "8610.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Before we entered across the Rhine, I had taken a Seder service in a place called Goch, between the Rhine and the Meuse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the brigadier who was in charge of supplies was somebody whom I had known because I-- whilst I was in England, I was stationed-- my wife and I were stationed with his sister.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we knew each other quite well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, of course, when he knew who I was, everything I wanted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He, he seconded his army catering officer to, to be of service to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we had a Seder service.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, that was a sort of thing that existed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a-- the padre was treated with tremendous respect.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And yet here was one chaplain to another that behaved so disgustingly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And yet when you get a man like Brigadier Glyn Hughes, whose behavior towards us was such that he felt a, a sense of brotherhood with these people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that here was a man who was stationed inside Germany and yet behaves like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, that's the sort of attitude that goes on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There's one other case-- I must mention this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "VE Day arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was an occasion for us to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I arranged that I should have a service in Hamburg, of all places, which was the nearest big town to, to, to, to Belsen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Well, I needed accommodation, a hall, a place to meet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Hamburg had been badly blitzed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I called on the office of the Burgermeister, so the mayor of Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But his deputy was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my best German, I asked him, what accommodation there was available?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't very helpful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, by the way, where are the synagogues in-- Oh, the synagogues?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were bombed by the British.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, oh, really?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
